T-010 is already fully implemented and committed. The implementation covers all acceptance criteria:

- **`render/rules/microtiming.py` is the only jitter source** — deterministic Gaussian via Box-Muller with SHA-256 seeding
- **σ values below JND** — enforced by `__post_init__` validation (raises if > 10 ms)
- **Grid-locked voices get σ=0** — `GRID_LOCKED_ROLES` frozenset maps drum/machine/perc/etc. to 0.0
- **Tests verify all of the above** — 12 tests covering σ by role, zero-jitter on grid-locked, distribution shape, determinism, and JND enforcement

No work needed — this task was completed in commits `0a08623` and `2eebebf`.
